subTasks FrontEnd

Creating initial front end views and funcions:
	2 input forms in: NewTask, TaskView
	
NewTask:
	New Card (Planned SubTasks)
	Inputs: (SubTask Name, est. hours, add button)
	View: Inline inputs form above subtasks list
		subtasks list item: (name, hours, type="planned", remove button)

	function: a list of subtasks inside the object sent by retrieveNewTaskInputs();
		subTasks: [{name, hours, type:"Planned"},..]
	

TaskView (tasksList): 
	Modal opened on click button in task view
	
	inputs: (subTask name, est. hours, type:"'Un Planned'/'Bug Fixing'", add button)
	
	view: Inline inputs form above subtasks list
		subtasks list item: (name, hours, type, remove button)
	
	function: 
		subtasks will be sent inside taskData same as tasklist preData
		additional functions: 
			add: call addSubTask(subTask) subTask:{taskID, name, hours, type}
			remove: call removeSubTask(subTask) subTask: {taskID, name}
			refresh list: a function to be called: fillSubTasksList(subTasks) subTasks: [{name, hours, type}, ..]
			fillSubTasksList(subTasks):
				called to remove all subtasks in the list and fill it again by the given subTasks.

	

